{
  "stem": "166.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 322.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With this card, I was safe, because other people had different colors of cards so they grabbed them away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father had a different color of a card, so they took him first to camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They grabbed him on, on the street, and he went to camp first, and I remained home with my mother and sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was pink or red.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It meant that he was working-- but his card did not produce anything for the, for the German Wehrmacht, for the German army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Electrical work was for material for the industry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working at that time in an electrical store where they were only packing supplies and send it to Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Electrical supplies-- and this was for German industry, going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had a card that I was-- used-- it was more to the benefit for the Germans, because they needed me for the industry.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later, and later on, they needed more people, where I went through a commission.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took me in that I'm going to be sent, but I was too young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they sent me back, back to work there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day-- every day the, the-- every time the German SS gave orders to the Jewish community center to give a quota of people to transport away.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So in the beginning they took the sick ones, the crazy ones, the people who were less, less educated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Jewish police went door to door with a list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They knocked on the door, middle of the night, because people would lock themselves up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't want to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they went to the houses to, to grab them in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
